metaforRCode.rawtext:
effectSizeVarianceCovarianceMatrix <- vcalc(
	vi = samplingVariance,
	data = dataset,
	cluster = JaspColumn_17_Encoded,
	obs = JaspColumn_5_Encoded,
	rho = list(0.7, 0.5),
	type = JaspColumn_2_Encoded
)

fit <- rma.mv(
	yi = JaspColumn_21_Encoded,
	V = effectSizeVarianceCovarianceMatrix,
	data = dataset,
	mods = ~JaspColumn_2_Encoded,
	random = list(`Component 1` = ~1 | JaspColumn_17_Encoded/JaspColumn_5_Encoded),
	method = 'REML',
	test = 't',
	level = 95
)

fit <- robust(
	fit,
	cluster = JaspColumn_17_Encoded,
	clubSandwich = TRUE,
	adjust = TRUE
)
